Starting off TY they were 16. 
Unfortunately this is might be no more :( A girl in my class is being deported back to Nigeria. Ridiculous. I know some of your are thinking 'well she iggeal, get rid of her'...well that's rubbish. She did a really good J.C and has been living in Ireland for the last 4/5years and SHOULD'T go. Everyone at school is going to try their best to stop this. I hope it works. Nearly everyone started crying today when we got the news we were so shocked.

That me stpry for the day
Jackie
